create a list/dict/array per provider in its class
in click, add provider specific options and let these be populated by looping over the class dict.

see code below for inspiration:


>>> from genomepy.provider import ProviderBase
>>> ProviderBase.list_providers()
dict_keys(['Ensembl', 'UCSC', 'NCBI'])
>>> ProviderBase.create("Ensembl")
<genomepy.provider.EnsemblProvider object at 0x7f5a42340278>
>>> for name in ProviderBase.list_providers():
...     p = ProviderBase.create(name)
...     for opion in p.options:
...